%N A015998 Inverse of 1989th cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A015998 Periodic with period length 1989. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 07 2017
%H A015998 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A015998/b015998.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..2000</a>
%H A015998 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>, period 1989.
